cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CY

This paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning techniques to extract PICO elements from medical literature. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with NLP and related topics. The paper also involves feature engineering and classification, which are common topics in cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper deals with medical data, which could also fall under cs.CY (Computers and Society).
